@node "Registration" "Registration"
@{fg shine}@{bg fill} Registration@{fg text}@{bg back}
 The unregistered demo-version has several disadvantages
 compared to the full version:
 · no time-lapse support
 · time limited to 6 updates
 · DEMO-text on all images
 · a requester needing your input at start
 · no FPU-version of the fsgfx.library
 · no PPC- and 040-version of the JPEG-saver
 Please consider registering for only 99 DM/66 US$ and support
 this product. To register, fill out the registration form and
 print it. Then send it to:

 Felix Schwarz
 Am Gründla 3
 D-91074 Herzogenaurach
 Germany

 Thank you for your support.

@endnode
